data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers***10K SELLER CREDIT TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR BUY DOWN INTEREST RATE***NEW PRICE REDUCTION***SELLER MOTIVATED****BEAUTIFUL MOVE-IN READY FULLY FURNISHED POOL HOME in the highly sought after community of High Grove in the City of Clermont, FL is just minutes from Disney World! This home features an open concept with 4 Bedrooms, 3 Baths With 2 Owners Suites. As you walk into this home, you'll love the luxurious feeling for you and your guests to enjoy. At the front, there are two bedrooms that are joined by a Jack-n-Jill bathroom with each room having direct access to the bathroom. You'll love entertaining in the Family room with open views of the fully updated kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The kitchen area is very spacious & has plenty of cabinet and counter space as well as an eat-in dining area. Two Owner’s Suites with en-suites sit towards the rear corners of the home just off of the patio area with each having their own individual access to the Pool. Through the sliding doors you will love the private patio and screened in resort style POOL and SPA. This home boasts a Tile Roof and Mature Landscaping and comes Fully furnished and is move-in ready for those looking for the perfect new home, Airbnb, Vacation home or Investment property.  The Gated Community has a large Clubhouse perfect for gatherings or a relaxing day at the Community pool and hot tub, movie room with games, fitness center, playroom, pool table and more. There is a playground right outside the Clubhouse with a small miniature golf area. HOA fees include lawn and shrub maintenance and irrigation, Valet garbage can service, use of amenities and clubhouse as well as a 24-hour community gate. The community is ideally located just 10 miles from Disney and minutes from most Orlando attractions and just 10 minutes south of the new 250-acre, $1.4 Billion Olympus sports training facility. Quick access to shopping, restaurants, medical and major highways. A/C unit replaced in 2020 and pool heater replaced in 2021. Make this gorgeous home your own as a year-round oasis or use as a Vacation Home or Airbnb. Short-term rentals are allowed! Your Florida home awaits you!
